  "subject": "Trigger doc jobs for files also outside of doc dir",
  "commit_message": "Trigger doc jobs for files also outside of doc dir\n\ndoc directory may contain symlinks to files stored in other\ndirectories. Taken into account that gerrit does not resolve any\nsymlinks it's better to trigger doc jobs for all .rst files in\nrepositories containing documentation instead of triggering the jobs\nonly for those inside doc directory.\n\nIssue-ID: SECCOM-239\nSigned-off-by: Krzysztof Opasiak <k.opasiak@samsung.com>\nChange-Id: I4bb8528e3dc9b6005eec84b6d3ad3023c7fc1ec7\n",
